#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.184"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.184:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.184:0.2"
msgid "19. Brāhmaṇavagga"
msgstr "19. Brahmins"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: jāṇussonīsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.184:0.3"
msgid "184. Abhayasutta"
msgstr "184. Fearless"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: jāṇussoṇi → jāṇussonī (bj)
msgctxt "an4.184:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the brahmin Jāṇussoṇi went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

msgctxt "an4.184:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:2.1"
msgid "“Ahañhi, bho gotama, evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhi:"
msgstr "“Master Gotama, this is my doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "an4.184:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘natthi yo maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassā’”ti."
msgstr "‘All those liable to death are frightened and terrified of death.’”"

msgctxt "an4.184:2.3"
msgid ""
"“Atthi, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa;"
msgstr ""
"“Brahmin, some of those liable to death are frightened and terrified of "
"death."

msgctxt "an4.184:2.4"
msgid ""
"atthi pana, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa."
msgstr ""
"But some of those liable to death are not frightened and terrified of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.174"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:3.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa?"
msgstr "Who are those frightened of death?"

msgctxt "an4.184:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, brāhmaṇa, ekacco kāmesu avītarāgo hoti avigatacchando avigatapemo "
"avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who isn’t free of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and "
"craving for sensual pleasures."

msgctxt "an4.184:3.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati."
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill,"

msgctxt "an4.184:3.4"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they think:"

msgctxt "an4.184:3.5"
msgid "‘piyā vata maṃ kāmā jahissanti, piye cāhaṃ kāme jahissāmī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The sensual pleasures that I love so much will leave me, and I’ll leave "
"them.’"

msgctxt "an4.184:3.6"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into "
"confusion."

msgctxt "an4.184:3.7"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa."
msgstr "This is someone who is frightened of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco kāye avītarāgo hoti avigatacchando "
"avigatapemo avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, it’s someone who isn’t free of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, "
"passion, and craving for the body."

msgctxt "an4.184:4.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati."
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill,"

msgctxt "an4.184:4.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they think:"

msgctxt "an4.184:4.4"
msgid "‘piyo vata maṃ kāyo jahissati, piyañcāhaṃ kāyaṃ jahissāmī’ti."
msgstr "‘This body that I love so much will leave me, and I’ll leave it.’"

msgctxt "an4.184:4.5"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into "
"confusion."

msgctxt "an4.184:4.6"
msgid ""
"Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa."
msgstr "This, too, is someone who is frightened of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco akatakalyāṇo hoti akatakusalo "
"akatabhīruttāṇo katapāpo kataluddo katakibbiso."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, it’s someone who hasn’t done good and skillful things that keep "
"them safe, but has done bad, violent, and corrupt things."

msgctxt "an4.184:5.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati."
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill,"

msgctxt "an4.184:5.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they think:"

msgctxt "an4.184:5.4"
msgid "‘akataṃ vata me kalyāṇaṃ, akataṃ kusalaṃ, akataṃ bhīruttāṇaṃ;"
msgstr "‘Well, I haven’t done good and skillful things that keep me safe."

msgctxt "an4.184:5.5"
msgid "kataṃ pāpaṃ, kataṃ luddaṃ, kataṃ kibbisaṃ."
msgstr "And I have done bad, violent, and corrupt things."

msgctxt "an4.184:5.6"
msgid ""
"Yāvatā, bho, akatakalyāṇānaṃ akatakusalānaṃ akatabhīruttāṇānaṃ katapāpānaṃ "
"kataluddānaṃ katakibbisānaṃ gati taṃ gatiṃ pecca gacchāmī’ti."
msgstr ""
"When I depart, I’ll go to the place where people who’ve done such things go.’"

msgctxt "an4.184:5.7"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into "
"confusion."

msgctxt "an4.184:5.8"
msgid ""
"Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa."
msgstr "This, too, is someone who is frightened of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco kaṅkhī hoti vicikicchī aniṭṭhaṅgato "
"saddhamme."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, it’s someone who’s doubtful, uncertain, and undecided about the "
"true teaching."

msgctxt "an4.184:6.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati."
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill,"

msgctxt "an4.184:6.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they think:"

msgctxt "an4.184:6.4"
msgid "‘kaṅkhī vatamhi vicikicchī aniṭṭhaṅgato saddhamme’ti."
msgstr "‘I’m doubtful, uncertain, and undecided about the true teaching.’"

msgctxt "an4.184:6.5"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into "
"confusion."

msgctxt "an4.184:6.6"
msgid ""
"Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa."
msgstr "This, too, is someone who is frightened of death."

msgctxt "an4.184:6.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, brāhmaṇa, cattāro maraṇadhammā samānā bhāyanti, santāsaṃ āpajjanti "
"maraṇassa."
msgstr ""
"These are the four people liable to death who are frightened and terrified "
"of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.175"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:7.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa?"
msgstr "Who are those not frightened of death?"

msgctxt "an4.184:7.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, brāhmaṇa, ekacco kāmesu vītarāgo hoti vigatacchando vigatapemo "
"vigatapipāso vigatapariḷāho vigatataṇho."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who is rid of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and "
"craving for sensual pleasures."

msgctxt "an4.184:7.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati."
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill,"

msgctxt "an4.184:7.4"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa na evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they don’t think:"

msgctxt "an4.184:7.5"
msgid "‘piyā vata maṃ kāmā jahissanti, piye cāhaṃ kāme jahissāmī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The sensual pleasures that I love so much will leave me, and I’ll leave "
"them.’"

msgctxt "an4.184:7.6"
msgid ""
"So na socati na kilamati na paridevati, na urattāḷiṃ kandati, na sammohaṃ "
"āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"They don’t sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into "
"confusion."

msgctxt "an4.184:7.7"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa."
msgstr "This is someone who’s not frightened of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:8.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco kāye vītarāgo hoti vigatacchando "
"vigatapemo vigatapipāso vigatapariḷāho vigatataṇho."
msgstr ""
