"maraṇassa."
msgstr "This, too, is someone who’s not frightened of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:9.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco akatapāpo hoti akataluddo akatakibbiso "
"katakalyāṇo katakusalo katabhīruttāṇo."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, it’s someone who hasn’t done bad, violent, and corrupt deeds, "
"but has done good and skillful deeds that keep them safe."

msgctxt "an4.184:9.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati."
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill,"

msgctxt "an4.184:9.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they think:"

msgctxt "an4.184:9.4"
msgid "‘akataṃ vata me pāpaṃ, akataṃ luddaṃ, akataṃ kibbisaṃ;"
msgstr "‘Well, I haven’t done bad, violent, and corrupt things."

msgctxt "an4.184:9.5"
msgid "kataṃ kalyāṇaṃ, kataṃ kusalaṃ, kataṃ bhīruttāṇaṃ."
msgstr "And I have done good and skillful deeds that keep me safe."

msgctxt "an4.184:9.6"
msgid ""
"Yāvatā, bho, akatapāpānaṃ akataluddānaṃ akatakibbisānaṃ katakalyāṇānaṃ "
"katakusalānaṃ katabhīruttāṇānaṃ gati taṃ gatiṃ pecca gacchāmī’ti."
msgstr ""
"When I depart, I’ll go to the place where people who’ve done such things go.’"

msgctxt "an4.184:9.7"
msgid ""
"So na socati na kilamati na paridevati, na urattāḷiṃ kandati, na sammohaṃ "
"āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"They don’t sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into "
"confusion."

msgctxt "an4.184:9.8"
msgid ""
"Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati "
"maraṇassa."
msgstr "This, too, is someone who’s not frightened of death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.176"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:10.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco akaṅkhī hoti avicikicchī niṭṭhaṅgato "
"saddhamme."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, it’s someone who’s not doubtful, uncertain, or undecided about "
"the true teaching."

