msgstr "This, too, is someone who’s not frightened of death."

msgctxt "an4.184:10.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, brāhmaṇa, cattāro maraṇadhammā samānā na bhāyanti, na santāsaṃ "
"āpajjanti maraṇassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the four people liable to death who are not frightened and "
"terrified of death.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an4.184:11.1"
msgid ""
"“Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ "
"gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Excellent, Master Gotama! … From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember "
"me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.184:11.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
